## Deferred: Open Multilingual Wordnet / CILI (Bond et al. tooling path)

**Not in the shipped app** unless there is an explicit product decision: linking rows to **OMW synsets** or **CILI** ids would enable hypernyms, definitions, and sense inventories, but it adds bundle or network complexity and fights the A1 “one card, one word” Study flow ([UX.md](UX.md) Map is visual progress only).

**Acceptable later (authoring-only):** offline lookup by English lemma or `concept` to suggest `mapGroup` neighbors or missing senses—human still commits changes to `words.ts` (or a topic module re-exported from there). Do not import TUFS dumps wholesale (different L1 design and language set than this project’s `EN`–`IT` core).
